"order to instantiate the aggregator device. It can be set back to 0 to "
"destroy the virtual device. The module will synchronously wait for the new "
"aggregator device to be successfully probed and if this doesn't happen, "
"writing to ``'live'`` will result in an error. This is a different behaviour "
"from the case when you create it using sysfs ``new_device`` interface."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/gpio/gpio-aggregator.rst:148
msgid ""
