"and appear as ``/config/gpio-aggregator/_sysfs.<N>/``. You cannot add or "
"remove line directories with mkdir(2)/rmdir(2). To modify lines, you must "
"use the \"delete_device\" interface to tear down the existing device and "
"reconfigure it from scratch. However, you can still toggle the aggregator "
"with the ``live`` attribute and adjust the ``key``, ``offset``, and ``name`` "
"attributes for each line when ``live`` is set to 0 by hand (i.e. it's not "
"waiting for deferred probe)."
